啤酒：
2元钱1瓶
4个瓶盖换1瓶
2个空瓶换一瓶

问：
10元最多可以喝几瓶？
var cap = 5;
var bottle = 5;
var num = 5;
while(cap>=4||bottle>=2){
 num=num+Math.floor(cap/4)+Math.floor(bottle/2);
 var t = cap;
 var s = bottle;
 cap = t- (Math.floor(t/4))*4 + Math.floor(t/4)+Math.floor(s/2);
 bottle = s - (Math.floor(bottle/2))*2 + Math.floor(t/4)+Math.floor(s /2);
};
num
15
